column2: IDEA-139903 TaskManagement: Trello: Change 'number' placeholder in commit message

column3: Have you submitted a contributor license agreement? If not, please download the PDF from http://www.jetbrains.org/display/IJOS/Contributor+Agreement and then print it out, sign (mention you github account name there), scan and email to contribute@jetbrains.com
Not yet, I'll when I get my hands on a printer (is printing out the document absolutely needed by the way?)
If you already have your signature scanned, you can insert it to the document image. But the signature is necessary.
The e-mail was just sent! Let me know if there's any problem :)
@maximethebault I see no problems here. Thanks!
